      <div class="accordion-content">
        <p>CFO Services provide strategic financial guidance typically offered by a Chief Financial Officer, but on an outsourced or part-time basis. These services include financial planning, budgeting, forecasting, cash flow management, and performance analysis. They are ideal for small to medium-sized businesses, startups, or organizations that need high-level financial expertise without hiring a full-time CFO.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="accordion-item" id="faq1">
    <div class="accordion-title">
      <div class="accordion-title-text">What specific services does your CFO Services business offer?</div>
