        src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/684c19327b327e58d058855f/684c19327b327e58d058864c_interface-icon-chevron-down.svg"
        alt="chevron down icon"
        class="accordion-icon"
      >
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-content-wrapper">
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <p>Our CFO Services include:<br>
i. Financial Strategy: Developing long-term financial plans aligned with your business goals.<br>
ii. Budgeting & Forecasting: Creating detailed budgets and financial forecasts to guide decision-making.<br>
iii. Cash Flow Management: Optimizing cash flow to ensure liquidity and operational stability.<br>
iv. Financial Reporting: Preparing customized reports, including profit & loss, balance sheets, and KPIs.<br>
v. Fundraising Support: Assisting with investor pitches, financial modeling, and capital-raising strategies.<br>
vi. Risk Management: Identifying and mitigating financial risks.<br>
vii. Compliance & Governance: Ensuring adherence to financial regulations and best practices.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

